data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged.  Within the gates of the tropical paradise called Forest Creek sits this spacious home with huge lot and lake views. Plenty of room for your family and friends to enjoy including 3 bedrooms, office/den, two living spaces, and no carpet. The open kitchen/family room combination offers upgraded cabinetry, beautiful granite countertops, center island breakfast bar, newer tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances and beautiful views of private back yard through sliding glass doors at the end of the large family room. Situated adjacent to the kitchen is a light and bright office/den that could be used as an additional bedroom. The primary suite overlooks the private back yard and offers large walk-in closet, oversized walk-in shower, white cabinets and high eyelash window for plenty of light. 2-car garage has epoxy floor. Enjoy evenings on the screened lanai while watching the various birds enjoying the peaceful lake views. Bring your design ideas and make this home yours! Forest Creek is one of Parrish’s premier Neal Communities situated on over 135 acres of land and offering nature/walking trails, a clubhouse including heated pool & spa, fitness center, outdoor grill, meeting space. Canoe and Kayakers can enjoy the 18-acre lake, gazebos, playground, sports courts. Golf carts welcome! 2 dog parks for your 4-legged friends! Plenty of shopping and dining options are within a 5-minute drive, 3 airports within 45 minutes plus a short commute to Lakewood Ranch, Bradenton, Tampa, St. Pete and Sarasota.
